column1:
According to the classification suggested by the international COMPON group, all organizations were classified according to some specific criteria, namely:
•	Year of data collection
•	Organization type and subtype
•	Geographic coverage
Within the category type and subtype of organization, the segregation by five main groups was proposed, namely: Political System, Science, Business, Civil Society and Media. Therefore, the segregation by groups was also considered as a relevant parameter for the description and presentation of the results.
